</ul>
<dl>
<dt><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada"><img alt="Flag of Canada" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Flag_of_Canada.svg/22px-Flag_of_Canada.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada">Canada</a></dt>
