<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Ontario" title="Ontario"><img alt="Flag of Ontario" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/88/Flag_of_Ontario.svg/22px-Flag_of_Ontario.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Ontario_Human_Rights_Code" title="Ontario Human Rights Code">Ontario Human Rights Code</a> 1962</li>
